title: Thursday Post Show (11-4-21)
itunes:title: Thursday Post Show (11-4-21)
description:
Bobby starts by a prank that got played on Amy yesterday with some station liners reading funny names. Kim Kardashian was spotted again with Pete Davidson…we wonder if it’s a real thing. We play artists singing “this is the Bobby Bones Show” and if we can identify the artist. We talk about anti-hero TV shows after a teacher was acquitted of making meth.
